high_descs: Turn to the right and stop at the counter on the left of the oven
Grab the small knife off of the counter
Turn around and head to the sink
Cut the tomato into slices
Turn around and head to the oven
Put the knife into the pan on the bottom right stove
Turn around and head to the sink
Grab one of the tomato slices
Turn around and head to the oven
Put the tomato in the bowl in the top left stove
Grab the bowl off of the stove
Turn left and head to the white table
Place the bowl on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting a bowl with a sliced tomato on the white table

high_descs: Turn right and face the counter on your right.
Take the knife from the counter in front of you under the paper towel roll.
Turn around and go towards the sink in front of you.
Slice the tomato in front of you on the sink.
Turn around and head towards the stove.
Put the knife in the pot on the stove.
Turn around and head towards the sink in front of you.
Take a tomato slice from the sink.
Turn around and head towards the stove in front of you.
Put the tomato slice in the pot with the knife in front of you on the stove.
Take the pot with the tomato and knife from the stove.
Turn left and face the table on the right.
Put the pot with the knife and tomato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a tomato slice in it on a table.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife located between the roll of paper towels and the front of the counter.
Turn around and walk in the direction of the sink.
Slice the left half of the tomato located to the left of the sink in sections perpendicular to the front of the counter on which it is located.
Turn around and walk towards the stove.
Place the knife upright with the handle down in the pan on the left back burner of the stove.
Turn around and walk towards the tomato to the left of the sink.
Pick up the center slice of the tomato.
Turn around and walk to the stove.
Place the tomato slice next to the knife in the pan on the left rear burner of the stove.
Pick up the pan containing the knife and the tomato.
Turn and walk towards the door, stop and face the table to the right of the front of the door.
Place the pan on the right side rear of the table with the knife and tomato on the inside of the bowel that is nearest the center line of the table.
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato with a knife, place it in a bowl, bring it to the table

high_descs: Turn and face counter with the coffee maker
Grab the knife that is in front of the coffee maker
Turn around and head to the sink
Cut the tomato at the sink into slices
Turn around and head to the oven
Put the knife into the bowl in the top left stove
Turn around and head to the sink
Grab one of the tomato slices
Turn around and head to the oven
Put the tomato in the bowl in the top left stove
Grab the bowl from the top left stove
Turn left and head to the white table
Put the bowl on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting a bowl with a knife and tomato slice onto the white table
